Description: Jinhui Shipping and Transportation Ltd is an investment holding company mainly engaged in the provision of marine transportation services. The Company is principally engaged in the ship chartering and ship owning businesses. The Company is also engaged in the ship management business. In addition, the Company is engaged in the operation of fleets of dry bulk carriers which are either used for carrying cargoes or time chartered-out to other shipping operators. Besides, the Company is engaged in the other shipping operating business, investment properties business, disposal of properties, plants and equipment and others. The Company operates its business in domestic and overseas markets such as Singapore, Ireland, South Korea, Thailand and others.
